---
<p class="fd-paragraph">
  A living, AI-maintained patient record that aggregates clinical history, communication preferences, care gaps, and risk signals in real time. Agents continuously update and act on the profile — no manual data entry required.
</p>

<h2 class="fd-section-heading">What it does</h2>
<ul class="fd-list">
  <li class="fd-list-item">Aggregates data from EHR, claims, and communication history into a single view</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">Surfaces active care gaps, risk scores, and next-best actions automatically</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">Updates in real time as agents complete tasks or interactions occur</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">Tracks communication preferences and engagement history per patient</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="fd-section-heading">Why it matters</h2>
<p class="fd-paragraph">
  Static patient records go stale the moment they're created. The Agentic Patient Profile is always current — because agents are always working.
</p>
